---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { LINKEDIN_URL } from '../consts';
---

<Base
  title="About"
  description="Riddam Jain — engineering leader in Rotterdam writing about cloud, AI, books, and leading teams."
>
  <h1>Hi, I'm Riddam 👋</h1>

  <p class="lead">
    I'm an engineering leader based in Rotterdam, working at Coolblue. I spend my
    days somewhere between the technical and the human side of building software —
    designing systems, growing engineers, and trying to keep both moving in the
    same direction.
  </p>

  <p>
    Most of my hands-on work lives around <strong>cloud and AI</strong> — building
    and operating systems on GCP and AWS, wrangling data and ML pipelines, and
    figuring out how to make AI genuinely useful in production rather than just
    impressive in a demo. I care a lot about the unglamorous parts: reliability,
    security, cost, and code that the next person can actually maintain.
  </p>

  <p>
    This blog is where I write things down. Partly to share what I've learned, and
    partly because writing is how I figure out what I actually think. You'll find a
    few different threads here:
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li>
      <a href="/engineering/"><strong>Engineering</strong></a> — deep dives and
      write-ups from real work: cloud architecture, AI-assisted development,
      tooling, and the occasional hard-won lesson.
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="/book-notes/"><strong>Book Notes</strong></a> — takeaways from books
      worth remembering, in my own words.
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="/leadership/"><strong>Leadership</strong></a> — thoughts on leading
      teams, growing engineers, and doing the job well.
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="/guides/"><strong>Study Guides</strong></a> — in-depth references
      I've built for certifications and core topics.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    If any of that resonates — or if you just want to disagree with me about
    something — I'd love to hear from you.
  </p>

  <p class="connect">
    <a href={LINKEDIN_URL}>Connect with me on LinkedIn →</a>
  </p>
</Base>

<style>
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .connect {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
